         <p class="lead text-justify">
            Currently we are trying to establish collaborations that would help us gain popularity and more traffic.
            Down
            below are going to appear people that we are working with. If you are intrested in a collaboration please
            give
            us a notice.
         </p>

         <div class="mt-4 d-flex flex-row justify-content-center flex-wrap">

            <div class="card mx-3 my-1 rounded-pill overflow-hidden" style="width: 11.5rem;">
               <a href="#izak">
                  <img src="/assets/collaboration/izak.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
               </a>
               <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title text-center lead">Izak</h5>
               </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mx-3 my-1 rounded-pill overflow-hidden" style="width: 11.5rem;">
               <a href="#pasha">
                  <img src="./assets/collaboration/pasha.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
               </a>
               <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title text-center lead">Pasha</h5>
               </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mx-3 my-1 rounded-pill overflow-hidden" style="width: 11.5rem;">
